{"tid":970773,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"好想飲咖啡奶茶","createTime":"2019-01-06T06:19:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-06T14:13:02.000Z","uid":78377,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4e683a8e024cc8c96a2cc28ac523e2a63e0ac0fe","tid":970773,"uid":78377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T06:19:17.000Z","msg":"見到好撚多新聞/討論話飲得多咖啡奶茶好傷身 <br />\n日日飲又會生腎者之石 <br />\n又或者會愈飲愈多 成癮<br />\n<br />\n自問係一個自制力高既人 <br />\n會㩒住自己可能一個星期最多飲三次左右 特別係開會之前 一日最多一杯<br />\n但有時係真心想嘆下一杯熱奶茶 熱咖啡 <br />\n有D滋味係其他飲品比唔到 <br />\n<br />\n有諗過飲其他野來代替 例如茶<br />\n但諗深一層 飲茶其實可以慢慢飲 唔覺唔覺係可以全日都飲茶<br />\n咁咪仲衰過我飲完一杯咖啡奶茶之後全日飲水<br />\n<br />\n有冇人可以話我知每日一杯咖啡奶茶 <br />\n其餘時間飲水 可唔可以抵銷到我既罪過"},{"pid":"f101b16c08501deb17c1f2f77bb4fe82d00bf924","tid":970773,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T06:20:33.000Z","msg":"一星期一杯 奶茶"},{"pid":"285cb1cb723f210353c91d3ffd97560908e5c1c6","tid":970773,"uid":78377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f101b16c08501deb17c1f2f77bb4fe82d00bf924","tid":970773,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T06:20:33.000Z","msg":"一星期一杯 奶茶"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T06:22:09.000Z","msg":"我好清楚自己係好難做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bec934627cf6c8306e605e674cf62de355bdb653","tid":970773,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"285cb1cb723f210353c91d3ffd97560908e5c1c6","tid":970773,"uid":78377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f101b16c08501deb17c1f2f77bb4fe82d00bf924","tid":970773,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T06:20:33.000Z","msg":"一星期一杯 奶茶"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T06:22:09.000Z","msg":"我好清楚自己係好難做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T06:45:31.000Z","msg":"咁2杯先"},{"pid":"dc0c0409235c5d9dba281a510dc5943c8f22a692","tid":970773,"uid":224107,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":